::Zardus::

Zardus frowns, looking at the console Feline was at. He nods. "Yes.... My 
future self had a similar system. The can come in usefull, yes...."

Realizing that she probably had no idea of what he was talking about when he 
reffered to his future self, Zardus turns back to the table.

"This replacement main proccessor should reset her internal functions though."

He reaches into Squizzy, fliqqing a switch on her proccessor, hoping it'd 
shut down her systems. He had gained alot of mechanical experience when he 
had built Delta, so he more or less knew what he was doing.
